data.title: West Chester University
data.meta_description: West Chester University, located in southeastern PA, is a public, regional institution committed to high-quality undergraduate, graduate, and doctoral programs.
data.text:
Video description (this video does not have audio) for the video above:

Scene 1: Marching band in a parade. Camera pointing at front of the band. Banner reads "West Chester University Incomparable Golden Rams". Camera pans to the rightand we see the colorguard doing a flag routine. Camera pans back to the left.

Scene 2: Female student looking into a microscope.

Scene 3: In the foreground, two female students and a male student are sitting at a table in a lounge. Each has a lapto. In the background, we see four students also sitting at another table. One has a laptop.

Scene 4: An overhead view of the football stadium showing the full track and football field. WCU is painted in the one endzone and Golden Rams in the other. The ram head logo is at the 50 yard line.

Scene 5: Music keyboard lab with a teacher at the front and 4 students. Each keyboard is connected to an Apple computer. Camera slowly moves inward as we can see the professor speaking.

Scene 6: Rammy standing at the archway of Philips. Rammy claps and then waves with his right arm in the air.

Scene 7: Three students with a close up of one student working on a laptop.
